		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey,
<br />
<br />Some friends asked me yesterday to make them NWC repros. Is there any hacks or patches to get the NWC running in any form on a common mapper board or is that repro from retrozone the only option? I could have sworn I've seen others showing off nwc repro's before that one came for sale on retrozone. I understand that it might not be running in all it's glory but the people that asked me are not looking to drop $100 bucks on a repro so if there is a scaled down\watered down solution these folks will be more than happy with it.
<br />
<br />Thanks,
<br />
<br />Shawn

		

