	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It would be possible in theory to mapper-hack NWC to run on a less-rare board, but the automatic switching among games would need a <em>lot</em> more programming work than the Forbidden Four.
<br />
<br />If your friends play NWC, what strategies do they use? Do they blow through SMB1 and Rad Racer to play more Tetris? (In that case, make them a repro of LJ65.) Or do they play SMB1 avoiding coins and rack up points on the various turtle-on-stairs glitch screens? (In that case, get them SMB1+Duck Hunt.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


